on-arrival: political_capital += 3; alquimia_expuesta = 1

The stenographers take it all down; the Diario de los Debates becomes the count's tombstone and its backup. When the packets burn in 1991 — and they will — the numbers will already live where fire is not jurisdiction. The next reform, and the one after that, will be drafted by men who remember this afternoon with fear. It is not victory. It is the receipt.
